l-tools (28 pass), llm-tasks (151 pass)\n    31→- **Builds**: groceryGenius, pezantTools, runeval — all passing\n    32→- **Open PRs**: waymo-sim #9 (Fix Build Backend) — already merged\n    33→- **Uncommitted work**: none across all repos\n    34→- **Autonomous dev logs**: no failures noted\n    35→\n    36→### Fixed\n    37→- Nothing — all clear.\n    38→\n...\n</persisted-output>"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ef2367bf-f903-4eac-b02b-2b3cc06ea55b","uuid":"a3503ac5-e609-4908-9261-15df80d0f476","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:20:45.629Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"REDACTED_REPOS_ROOT/auto-dev/fix-checker/logs/failures.md","content":"# Fix Checker Failure Log\n\nEach entry is appended by the fix-checker agent after every run.\nThis log helps identify recurring issues and track what's been checked.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-19 — Run 1\n\n### Checked\n- **All repos**: builds, tests, git status, open PRs\n- **PM2**: all processes online (no issues)\n- **Test results**: groceryGenius (81 pass), pezantTools (51 pass), runeval (53 pass), promptlibrary (66 pass), valueSortify (38 pass), job-scraper (59 pass), activity-tracker (44 pass), social-tools (28 pass), llm-tasks (151 pass), waymo-sim (32 pass after fix)\n- **Builds**: groceryGenius, pezantTools, runeval — all passing\n- **Open PRs**: none across all repos\n\n### Fixed\n- **waymo-sim**: Invalid `build-backend` in `pyproject.toml` — was `setuptools.backends._legacy:_Backend` (nonexistent), changed to `setuptools.build_meta`. This prevented `pip install` and blocked all 32 tests from running. PR #10, auto-merged.\n\n### Notes\n- Git push via HTTPS still silently fails on some repos; used `gh api` to create remote ref (known issue from Run 20)\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-19 — Run 2\n\n### Checked\n- **All repos**: builds, tests, git status, open PRs\n- **PM2**: all 11 processes online (no issues, restart counts normal)\n- **Test results**: groceryGenius (81 pass), pezantTools (51 pass), runeval (5